'''BND''' may stand for:* ''Bundesnachrichtendienst'', German intelligence agency* Bank of North Dakota* Buy Nothing Day* Brunei dollar (ISO currency code)* BTEC National Diploma* Brandon railway station, Brandon, Suffolk, England; National Rail station code BND* Bulgarian New Democracy, a Bulgarian centre-right party* "BND", a song on ''No Doubt'' (No Doubt album)* VID (company) (ВИD), a Russian TV company, as they represent the Cyrillic acronym of that company